phi-adapter-sdk (0.1.3-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Remove Qt helper build and packaging from base SDK repo.
  * Keep base SDK repository and packages free of Qt build dependencies.

 -- Marius Schumacher <marius.schumacher@phisys.com>  Sun, 08 Mar 2026 12:00:00 +0000

phi-adapter-sdk (0.1.2-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Require Qt6 base development package for qt helper package builds.
  * Enable qt helper target explicitly during Debian package configuration.
  * Fail package install split when phi_adapter_sdk_qt is missing instead of generating empty qt packages.

 -- Marius Schumacher <marius.schumacher@phisys.com>  Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:25:00 +0000

phi-adapter-sdk (0.1.1-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Split Qt helper out into a dedicated shared library package (phi-adapter-sdk-qt).
  * Add dedicated CMake config and export set for phi-adapter-sdk-qt.
  * Move Qt headers and Qt CMake targets to Qt-specific install package.
  * Keep base runtime package clean and Qt-free.

 -- Marius Schumacher <marius.schumacher@phisys.com>  Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:10:00 +0000

